(4588, 251, 'page_builder_1_content_block_0_contents', '<h3>Let our dedicated technicians tend to your business\' needs</h3>\r\nWith over 50 years\' experience, our dedicated electricians are here to tend to your business\' needs. Whether it\'s electrical design, new installation, rewiring, maintenance or testing, you can depend on our services.'),
