(9971, 374, 'above_the_fold_main_page_content', 'Our family business is driven by a passion to deliver electrical contracting excellence to our customers. \r\nWith over 50 years of experience handling commercial, industrial, local authority and domestic projects, large and small, locally and nationally, we have what it takes to tackle even the most demanding of projects. \r\nKey to our continued success is the investment we make in growing a team of highly skilled and professionally qualified electrical engineers, who share our enthusiasm for putting customers first.'),
