(12083, 380, 'testimonials_0_contents', 'When our our domestic fuse box tripped and cut off all the electricity to the kitchen, I telephoned Unwin Electrics for some advice. On leaving a message with Gillian my call was returned within 10 minutes. Paul talked me through how to try to resolve the problem but when this didn\'t fix the issue, he immediately arranged for an engineer to come and have a look. On inspection the engineer quickly ascertained that a replacement part was needed to fix the problem and  immediately went back to get it, returning to fix the fault. Our supply was resumed within 4 hours of my original telephone call with minimum of fuss. I was really pleased with the prompt and efficient service and recommend this company should  you find yourself with a similar problem. Professional, friendly and efficient. '),
(12084, 380, '_testimonials_0_contents', 'field_5a992bf840e30'),
(12085, 380, 'testimonials_0_footnote', 'From Dawn McWhir, Loughborough'),
(12086, 380, '_testimonials_0_footnote', 'field_5a992c5840e31'),
(12087, 380, 'testimonials_1_contents', 'John Unwin Electrical has been working for the college for over 15 years, providing numerous electrical services including maintentance and repairs, inspections and testing and new build installations.  They have worked on the college estate both directly employed by the college and also sub contracting to main contractors appointed by the college to complete new capital investment projects. \r\nJohn Unwin Electrical Contractors provide a reliable, efficient and high quality professional service offering good value for money.  Its these attributes that the college is mindful of when selecting contractors and why Brooksby Melton College continues to employ the services of John Unwin Electrical. \r\nI would happily recommend John Unwin Electrical to estate colleagues within the educational sector.'),
(12088, 380, '_testimonials_1_contents', 'field_5a992bf840e30'),
(12089, 380, 'testimonials_1_footnote', 'Andy Pass, Head of Estates - Brooksby Melton College'),
(12090, 380, '_testimonials_1_footnote', 'field_5a992c5840e31'),
(12091, 380, 'testimonials_2_contents', 'Mr Unwin,  \r\nI would just like to say a very big thank you for the recent work that was carried out by yourselves in my home. Your very friendly and professional electrician Paul installed my new electric oven and on a previous occasion Paul also carried out electrical work in my house. \r\n On both occasions Paul worked very efficiently and to a high standard and was very polite and friendly too which was lovely. Whilst installing my new oven Paul even set the timer, clock etc so that I was all set to go! He even took away all the empty boxes as I was poorly at the time and I wasn\'t able to.   \r\nI have already recommended your company to my family and friends and will continue to do so without a doubt!'),
(12092, 380, '_testimonials_2_contents', 'field_5a992bf840e30'),
(12093, 380, 'testimonials_2_footnote', 'Thank you so much, Tracy Baker.'),
(12094, 380, '_testimonials_2_footnote', 'field_5a992c5840e31'),
(12095, 380, 'testimonials_3_contents', 'John Unwin Electrical Contractors have been working to rewire Noseley Hall.  It is the first time Ive used them and I will certainly go back to the for any future electrical work.  Their engineers are honest, hard working and respectful, they do everything they can to help the client.  I wouldnt have any hesitation in recommending John Unwin Electrical Contractors to anyone. '),
(12096, 380, '_testimonials_3_contents', 'field_5a992bf840e30'),
(12097, 380, 'testimonials_3_footnote', 'Lord Hazelrigg - Noseley Hall'),
(12098, 380, '_testimonials_3_footnote', 'field_5a992c5840e31'),
(12099, 380, 'testimonials_4_contents', 'We have worked on a number of projects with john Unwin Electrical from design and build to traditional contracts and we have found them to be helpful on site, able to discuss solutions to problems with ourselves and our clients allowing us to hand over a top quality installation.  The operatives on site are accommodating to the changes in programme and work well with other trades.  I would be happy to use Unwins again and would certainly recommend them for any type of project.'),
(12100, 380, '_testimonials_4_contents', 'field_5a992bf840e30'),
(12101, 380, 'testimonials_4_footnote', 'Lord Hazelrigg - Noseley Hall'),
